{
  "video_id": "YATYsgi3e5A",
  "title": "A new weapon in the fight against superbugs | David Brenner",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13928.0,
      "end_time": 17993.0,
      "text": "So ... we&#39;re in a real live war at the moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18170.0,
      "end_time": 20431.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a war that we&#39;re truly losing."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20970.0,
      "end_time": 22814.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a war on superbugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25692.0,
      "end_time": 27523.0,
      "text": "So you might wonder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27547.0,
      "end_time": 29605.0,
      "text": "if I&#39;m going to talk about superbugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29629.0,
      "end_time": 33861.0,
      "text": "why I&#39;m showing you a photograph of some soccer fans --"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33885.0,
      "end_time": 37105.0,
      "text": "Liverpool soccer fans celebrating a famous victory"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37130.0,
      "end_time": 39232.0,
      "text": "in Istanbul, a decade ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40233.0,
      "end_time": 42393.0,
      "text": "In the back, in the red shirt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42417.0,
      "end_time": 44400.0,
      "text": "well, that&#39;s me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44280.0,
      "end_time": 48559.0,
      "text": "and next to me in the red hat, that&#39;s my friend Paul Rice."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49168.0,
      "end_time": 52589.0,
      "text": "So a couple of years after this picture was taken,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52614.0,
      "end_time": 56451.0,
      "text": "Paul went into hospital for some minor surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56475.0,
      "end_time": 60748.0,
      "text": "and he developed a superbug-related infection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60772.0,
      "end_time": 62760.0,
      "text": "and he died."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62425.0,
      "end_time": 65173.0,
      "text": "And I was truly shocked."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65197.0,
      "end_time": 67612.0,
      "text": "He was a healthy guy in the prime of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68535.0,
      "end_time": 69904.0,
      "text": "So there and then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69928.0,
      "end_time": 73484.0,
      "text": "and actually with a lot of encouragement from a couple of TEDsters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73508.0,
      "end_time": 76719.0,
      "text": "I declared my own personal war on superbugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78365.0,
      "end_time": 80711.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s talk about superbugs for a moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80735.0,
      "end_time": 84119.0,
      "text": "The story actually starts in the 1940s"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84143.0,
      "end_time": 87214.0,
      "text": "with the widespread introduction of antibiotics."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 87925.0,
      "end_time": 89324.0,
      "text": "And since then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89348.0,
      "end_time": 93884.0,
      "text": "drug-resistant bacteria have continued to emerge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93908.0,
      "end_time": 97329.0,
      "text": "and so we&#39;ve been forced to develop newer and newer drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 97353.0,
      "end_time": 99225.0,
      "text": "to fight these new bacteria."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 100610.0,
      "end_time": 105956.0,
      "text": "And this vicious cycle actually is the origin of superbugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 105980.0,
      "end_time": 110414.0,
      "text": "which is simply bacteria for which we don&#39;t have effective drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 111474.0,
      "end_time": 115280.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure you&#39;ll recognize at least some of these superbugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 115520.0,
      "end_time": 117416.0,
      "text": "These are the more common ones around today."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 118158.0,
      "end_time": 122605.0,
      "text": "Last year, around 700,000 people died"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 122629.0,
      "end_time": 125369.0,
      "text": "from superbug-related diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 125983.0,
      "end_time": 129292.0,
      "text": "Looking to the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 129316.0,
      "end_time": 132452.0,
      "text": "if we carry on on the path we&#39;re going,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 132476.0,
      "end_time": 136102.0,
      "text": "which is basically a drugs-based approach to the problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 136126.0,
      "end_time": 138722.0,
      "text": "the best estimate by the middle of this century"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 138746.0,
      "end_time": 143596.0,
      "text": "is that the worldwide death toll from superbugs will be 10 million."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 144126.0,
      "end_time": 145563.0,
      "text": "10 million."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 145947.0,
      "end_time": 148758.0,
      "text": "Just to put that in context, that&#39;s actually more"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 148782.0,
      "end_time": 152317.0,
      "text": "than the number of people that died of cancer worldwide last year."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 152954.0,
      "end_time": 157100.0,
      "text": "So it seems pretty clear that we&#39;re not on a good road,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 157340.0,
      "end_time": 160947.0,
      "text": "and the drugs-based approach to this problem is not working."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 162247.0,
      "end_time": 164708.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a physicist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 164732.0,
      "end_time": 168669.0,
      "text": "and so I wondered, could we take a physics-based approach --"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 168693.0,
      "end_time": 170584.0,
      "text": "a different approach to this problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 171590.0,
      "end_time": 173122.0,
      "text": "And in that context,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 173146.0,
      "end_time": 175797.0,
      "text": "the first thing we know for sure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 175821.0,
      "end_time": 179154.0,
      "text": "is that we actually know how to kill every kind of microbe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 179178.0,
      "end_time": 180767.0,
      "text": "every kind of virus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 180791.0,
      "end_time": 182422.0,
      "text": "every kind of bacteria."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 182809.0,
      "end_time": 185370.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s with ultraviolet light."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 185505.0,
      "end_time": 188326.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve actually known this for more than 100 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 188933.0,
      "end_time": 191569.0,
      "text": "I think you all know what ultraviolet light is."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 191593.0,
      "end_time": 194631.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s part of a spectrum that includes infrared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 194656.0,
      "end_time": 196102.0,
      "text": "it includes visible light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 196126.0,
      "end_time": 200580.0,
      "text": "and the short-wavelength part of this group is ultraviolet light."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 201607.0,
      "end_time": 204696.0,
      "text": "The key thing from our perspective here"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 204720.0,
      "end_time": 209908.0,
      "text": "is that ultraviolet light kills bacteria by a completely different mechanism"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 209932.0,
      "end_time": 211804.0,
      "text": "from the way drugs kill bacteria."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 212605.0,
      "end_time": 218393.0,
      "text": "So ultraviolet light is just as capable of killing a drug-resistant bacteria"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 218417.0,
      "end_time": 220641.0,
      "text": "as any other bacteria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 220665.0,
      "end_time": 225143.0,
      "text": "and because ultraviolet light is so good at killing all bugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 225167.0,
      "end_time": 228302.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s actually used a lot these days to sterilize rooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 228326.0,
      "end_time": 231374.0,
      "text": "sterilize working surfaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 231398.0,
      "end_time": 234226.0,
      "text": "What you see here is a surgical theater"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 234250.0,
      "end_time": 238581.0,
      "text": "being sterilized with germicidal ultraviolet light."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 239578.0,
      "end_time": 242550.0,
      "text": "But what you don&#39;t see in this picture, actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 242790.0,
      "end_time": 243744.0,
      "text": "is any people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 243768.0,
      "end_time": 246400.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s a very good reason for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 246280.0,
      "end_time": 249614.0,
      "text": "Ultraviolet light is actually a health hazard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 249639.0,
      "end_time": 251964.0,
      "text": "so it can damage cells in our skin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 251988.0,
      "end_time": 253419.0,
      "text": "cause skin cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 253443.0,
      "end_time": 254954.0,
      "text": "it can damage cells in our eye,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 254978.0,
      "end_time": 258466.0,
      "text": "cause eye diseases like cataract."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 258490.0,
      "end_time": 261945.0,
      "text": "So you can&#39;t use conventional, germicidal, ultraviolet light"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 261969.0,
      "end_time": 263698.0,
      "text": "when there are people are around."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 263722.0,
      "end_time": 264936.0,
      "text": "And of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 264961.0,
      "end_time": 267991.0,
      "text": "we want to sterilize mostly when there are people around."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 268929.0,
      "end_time": 271595.0,
      "text": "So the ideal ultraviolet light"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 271620.0,
      "end_time": 275303.0,
      "text": "would actually be able to kill all bacteria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 275327.0,
      "end_time": 276863.0,
      "text": "including superbugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 276887.0,
      "end_time": 279401.0,
      "text": "but would be safe for human exposure."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 280312.0,
      "end_time": 284559.0,
      "text": "And actually that&#39;s where my physics background kicked into this story."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 285296.0,
      "end_time": 287488.0,
      "text": "Together with my physics colleagues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 287512.0,
      "end_time": 293587.0,
      "text": "we realized there actually is a particular wavelength of ultraviolet light"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 293611.0,
      "end_time": 296104.0,
      "text": "that should kill all bacteria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 296128.0,
      "end_time": 298288.0,
      "text": "but should be safe for human exposure."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 298928.0,
      "end_time": 302246.0,
      "text": "That wavelength is called far-UVC light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 302270.0,
      "end_time": 306563.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s just the short-wavelength part of the ultraviolet spectrum."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 307375.0,
      "end_time": 309506.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s see how that would work."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 310426.0,
      "end_time": 314235.0,
      "text": "What you&#39;re seeing here is the surface of our skin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 314259.0,
      "end_time": 318602.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to superimpose on that some bacteria in the air above the skin."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 319536.0,
      "end_time": 321203.0,
      "text": "Now we&#39;re going to see what happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 321227.0,
      "end_time": 326369.0,
      "text": "when conventional, germicidal, ultraviolet light impinges on this."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 327631.0,
      "end_time": 328780.0,
      "text": "So what you see is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 328805.0,
      "end_time": 334910.0,
      "text": "as we know, germicidal light is really good at killing bacteria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 334115.0,
      "end_time": 335425.0,
      "text": "but what you also see"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 335449.0,
      "end_time": 338792.0,
      "text": "is that it penetrates into the upper layers of our skin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 338816.0,
      "end_time": 341368.0,
      "text": "and it can damage those key cells in our skin"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 341392.0,
      "end_time": 344597.0,
      "text": "which ultimately, when damaged, can lead to skin cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 346108.0,
      "end_time": 348956.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s compare now with far-UVC light --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 348980.0,
      "end_time": 350140.0,
      "text": "same situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 350164.0,
      "end_time": 352646.0,
      "text": "skin and some bacteria in the air above them."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 354342.0,
      "end_time": 355594.0,
      "text": "So what you&#39;re seeing now"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 355618.0,
      "end_time": 360414.0,
      "text": "is that again, far-UVC light&#39;s perfectly fine at killing bacteria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 360438.0,
      "end_time": 364525.0,
      "text": "but what far-UVC light can&#39;t do is penetrate into our skin."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 365318.0,
      "end_time": 368320.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s a good, solid physics reason for that:"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 368570.0,
      "end_time": 373421.0,
      "text": "far-UVC light is incredibly, strongly absorbed by all biological materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 373445.0,
      "end_time": 375357.0,
      "text": "so it simply can&#39;t go very far."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 376680.0,
      "end_time": 380637.0,
      "text": "Now, viruses and bacteria are really, really, really small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 380661.0,
      "end_time": 385527.0,
      "text": "so the far-UVC light can certainly penetrate them and kill them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 385551.0,
      "end_time": 388935.0,
      "text": "but what it can&#39;t do is penetrate into skin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 388959.0,
      "end_time": 391361.0,
      "text": "and it can&#39;t even penetrate the dead-cell area"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 391385.0,
      "end_time": 393207.0,
      "text": "right at the very surface of our skin."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 393815.0,
      "end_time": 400137.0,
      "text": "So far-UVC light should be able to kill bacteria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 400161.0,
      "end_time": 401431.0,
      "text": "but kill them safely."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 403397.0,
      "end_time": 404563.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s the theory."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 404587.0,
      "end_time": 407299.0,
      "text": "It should work, should be safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 407921.0,
      "end_time": 409516.0,
      "text": "What about in practice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 409540.0,
      "end_time": 410691.0,
      "text": "Does it really work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 410715.0,
      "end_time": 412920.0,
      "text": "Is it really safe?"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 412599.0,
      "end_time": 415500.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s actually what our lab has been working on"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 415290.0,
      "end_time": 417246.0,
      "text": "the past five or six years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 417270.0,
      "end_time": 420119.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m delighted to say the answer to both these questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 420143.0,
      "end_time": 421323.0,
      "text": "is an emphatic yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 421348.0,
      "end_time": 422628.0,
      "text": "Yes, it does work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 422652.0,
      "end_time": 424310.0,
      "text": "but yes, it is safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 424460.0,
      "end_time": 426233.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m delighted to say that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 426257.0,
      "end_time": 428496.0,
      "text": "but actually I&#39;m not very surprised to say that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 428520.0,
      "end_time": 430791.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s purely the laws of physics at work."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 433911.0,
      "end_time": 436460.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s look to the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 436700.0,
      "end_time": 441828.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m thrilled that we now have a completely new weapon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 441852.0,
      "end_time": 445316.0,
      "text": "and I should say an inexpensive weapon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 445340.0,
      "end_time": 447839.0,
      "text": "in our fight against superbugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 448447.0,
      "end_time": 449695.0,
      "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 449719.0,
      "end_time": 452555.0,
      "text": "I see far-UVC lights in surgical theaters."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 453629.0,
      "end_time": 456958.0,
      "text": "I see far-UVC lights in food preparation areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 458460.0,
      "end_time": 460906.0,
      "text": "And in terms of preventing the spread of viruses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 460930.0,
      "end_time": 464102.0,
      "text": "I see far-UVC lights in schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 464126.0,
      "end_time": 466649.0,
      "text": "preventing the spread of influenza,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 466673.0,
      "end_time": 468638.0,
      "text": "preventing the spread of measles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 468662.0,
      "end_time": 472642.0,
      "text": "and I see far-UVC lights in airports or airplanes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 472666.0,
      "end_time": 476794.0,
      "text": "preventing the global spread of viruses like H1N1 virus."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 478150.0,
      "end_time": 480181.0,
      "text": "So back to my friend Paul Rice."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 480206.0,
      "end_time": 484101.0,
      "text": "He was actually a well-known and well-loved local politician"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 484125.0,
      "end_time": 486797.0,
      "text": "in his and my hometown of Liverpool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 486821.0,
      "end_time": 491250.0,
      "text": "and they put up a statue in his memory in the center of Liverpool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 491490.0,
      "end_time": 492344.0,
      "text": "and there it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 492368.0,
      "end_time": 494558.0,
      "text": "But me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 494582.0,
      "end_time": 499317.0,
      "text": "I want Paul&#39;s legacy to be a major advance in this war against superbugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 500200.0,
      "end_time": 502670.0,
      "text": "Armed with the power of light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 502910.0,
      "end_time": 504129.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s actually within our grasp."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 505297.0,
      "end_time": 506448.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 506472.0,
      "end_time": 511368.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 511392.0,
      "end_time": 514510.0,
      "text": "Chris Anderson: Stay up here, David, I&#39;ve got a question for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 514534.0,
      "end_time": 515948.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 517342.0,
      "end_time": 521928.0,
      "text": "David, tell us where you&#39;re up to in developing this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 521952.0,
      "end_time": 524899.0,
      "text": "and what are the remaining obstacles to trying to roll out"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 524923.0,
      "end_time": 526303.0,
      "text": "and realize this dream?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 526678.0,
      "end_time": 529869.0,
      "text": "David Brenner: Well, I think we now know that it kills all bacteria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 529893.0,
      "end_time": 531948.0,
      "text": "but we sort of knew that before we started,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 531972.0,
      "end_time": 534150.0,
      "text": "but we certainly tested that."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 534174.0,
      "end_time": 536888.0,
      "text": "So we have to do lots and lots of tests about safety,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 536912.0,
      "end_time": 540435.0,
      "text": "and so it&#39;s more about safety than it is about efficacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 540840.0,
      "end_time": 543244.0,
      "text": "And we need to do short-term tests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 543268.0,
      "end_time": 545271.0,
      "text": "and we need to do long-term tests"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 545295.0,
      "end_time": 549178.0,
      "text": "to make sure you can&#39;t develop melanoma many years on."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 549494.0,
      "end_time": 553374.0,
      "text": "So those studies are pretty well done at this point."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 553850.0,
      "end_time": 559232.0,
      "text": "The FDA of course is something we have to deal with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 559256.0,
      "end_time": 560631.0,
      "text": "and rightly so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 560655.0,
      "end_time": 564345.0,
      "text": "because we certainly can&#39;t use this in the real world without FDA approval."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 564766.0,
      "end_time": 567964.0,
      "text": "CA: Are you trying to launch first in the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 567988.0,
      "end_time": 569367.0,
      "text": "or somewhere else?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 569772.0,
      "end_time": 571924.0,
      "text": "DB: Actually, in a couple of countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 571948.0,
      "end_time": 575384.0,
      "text": "In Japan and in the US, both."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 575873.0,
      "end_time": 580478.0,
      "text": "CA: Have you been able to persuade biologists, doctors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 580502.0,
      "end_time": 582151.0,
      "text": "that this is a safe approach?"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 582612.0,
      "end_time": 585707.0,
      "text": "DB: Well, as you can imagine, there is a certain skepticism"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 585731.0,
      "end_time": 589299.0,
      "text": "because everybody knows that UV light is not safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 589691.0,
      "end_time": 591676.0,
      "text": "So when somebody comes along and says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 591700.0,
      "end_time": 595360.0,
      "text": "\"Well, this particular UV light is safe,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 595600.0,
      "end_time": 596702.0,
      "text": "there is a barrier to be crossed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 596726.0,
      "end_time": 598916.0,
      "text": "but the data are there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 598940.0,
      "end_time": 601631.0,
      "text": "and I think that&#39;s what we&#39;re going to be standing on."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 602487.0,
      "end_time": 604177.0,
      "text": "CA: Well, we wish you well."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 604201.0,
      "end_time": 606106.0,
      "text": "This is potentially such important work."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 606130.0,
      "end_time": 608163.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much for sharing this with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 608187.0,
      "end_time": 609338.0,
      "text": "Thank you, David."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 609362.0,
      "end_time": 612563.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}